[
  {
    "scene": "TitleScene",
    "file": "01-title.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "歡迎來到誰讓他煉器的！第二章，第二集，低語洞窟。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "邏輯修正小組成立後的第一個任務——探索後山的低語洞窟。聽說那裡住著一個上古大能的殘魂，已經嚇跑了十七批弟子。但周墨認為，這只是一個「待修復的離線終端」。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene1",
    "file": "02-content1.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "邏輯修正小組，第一次正式任務——低語洞窟探索。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我帶了投降表。三份。"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我帶了研究筆記。如果洞窟裡有女性殘魂，我要記錄單身光環的有效範圍。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "先進去再說。這個洞窟的結構很有規律，像是某種陣法構建的空間。"
      },
      {
        "character": "soul",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "吾乃上古劍仙——滄溟子！誰敢闖入吾之領地！"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "對不起對不起對不起！我投降！"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "有意思。一個語音觸發的自動防禦系統。讓我看看能不能重設密碼。"
      },
      {
        "character": "soul",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你說什麼？！吾乃——"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "找到了。能量核心有裂痕，記憶區段損壞。他只能重複同一句話。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene2",
    "file": "03-content2.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "所以這個上古劍仙其實是一個記憶體壞掉的人工智慧？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "更精確地說，是「靈魂驅動的自動防禦系統」。我來修復他。"
      },
      {
        "character": "soul",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你——你要修復吾？三千年来，你是第一個不逃跑的人。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "當然。這只是常規維護。修好了，以後別再大喊大叫。"
      },
      {
        "character": "soul",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "吾想起了……吾是滄溟子，問道宗第三代長老。吾把畢生修為煉成了一把劍——但是忘記放哪了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "三千年前的長老也忘東西？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "忘加位置標記是普遍性問題。不過至少他不再重複那句話了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "等一下，他煉的那把劍——煉器峰傳說中的「滄溟之劍」不會就是吧？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "有意思。那把劍被列為宗門至寶，但沒有人能拔出來。"
      },
      {
        "character": "soul",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "吾知道原因。吾當年……忘記加拔劍按鈕了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "原來忘加按鈕是家族遺傳。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "OutroScene",
    "file": "04-outro.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "感謝收看誰讓他煉器的！第二章第二集，低語洞窟。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "邏輯修正小組的第一個任務圓滿完成——殘魂被修好了，但那把「忘加拔劍按鈕」的滄溟之劍還在等著有人來拔。周墨已經在研究那個按鈕該怎麼加了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "下集預告：低語洞窟的事傳開了，長老派邏輯修正小組參加宗門秘境探索。別的宗門在破解上古禁制，周墨掏出了「雷射切割陣法」。長老說：「這不是禁制破解工具！」「但效率很高。」"
      }
    ]
  }
]
